room_title: Escape room "Empire City: Villain" by North Texas Escape Rooms in Dallas-Fort Worth
room_description: Dr. Beel is out of town finding some Chronomium, Captain X’s weakness. Now it is up to you, his minions, to show Dr. Beel you’re more valuable than he thinks you are. Dr. Beel needs one last thing to power his mind control machine...the Key to Empire City! Your goal is to steal the key to complete his evil plot. Do so quickly because you never know when Captain X and the X-League will show up!
